Reviews
Review by - Yelp
Terri M:
This restaurant is very good. I've been there with family before. I had the best fish and chips.
Review by - Yelp
Jasob C:
Blackened grouper sandwich was fantastic.   Loved the onion strings that they added. Service was great for an early lunch.
Review by - Yelp
Mike S:
Had a lovely evening here with three lovely ladies. The staff was very nice. The food was delicious, the drinks were ice cold and strong. I had the swordfish (the special for the night) it was grilled to perfection. Highly recommend to anyone in the area an in the mood for some nice seafood.
Review by - Yelp
Patrick H:
Went last night as a group of 4. Had a fantastic time! Waitress was awesome! We never had to wait for our drinks. Bang bang shrimp tacos were to die for! Band was very good as well. Would definitely go back!
Review by - Yelp
Alexis W:
The food came out super quickly and very well service. It was bingo night but we had no wait inside which is exactly what we wanted.
